              Was attempting to change my brakes and the passenger side front wheel was giving me some issues. Got a breaker bar and *SNAP* I'm not holding a lugnut in my hand. <br /><br />Do I have to replace the entire spindle or can I somehow just replace that bolt? <br /><br />This is on a 2006 Infiniti M35.

              

              
              
            </div>
